title: What do you want from me Riot?

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body:
Seriously! I warded, owned teamfights, helped with Baron and Dragon, stunned the entire team multiple times. Took towers, inhibitors built items correctly and all that shit.

A? A!?

#needtoventsomesalt

replies.body: Your farm is extremely low for a 55 minute game.
